short.am,ar,de,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es,es_4: This extension enables users to export Shopify data in CSV or Excel formats.
short.bg: Този разширение позволява на потребителите да експортират данни от Shopify в CSV или Excel формат.
short.bn: এই এক্সটেনশন ব্যবহারকারীদের শপিফাই ডেটা এক্সপোর্ট করতে সক্ষম করে CSV বা এক্সেল ফরম্যাটে।
short.ca: Aquesta extensió permet als usuaris exportar dades de Shopify en formats CSV o Excel.
short.cs: Tato rozšíření umožňují uživatelům exportovat data z Shopify ve formátech CSV nebo Excel.
short.da: Denne udvidelse giver brugerne mulighed for at eksportere Shopify-data i CSV- eller Excel-formater.
short.zh_CN: 此扩展允许用户将 Shopify 数据导出为 CSV 或 Excel 格式。

long.am,ar,de,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es,es_4: This extension is a powerful tool for business owners, market analysts, and researchers who need to collect and analyze data from Shopify stores. By automating the data extraction process and providing easy-to-use export options, the extension saves time and effort, allowing users to focus on data analysis and strategic decision-making. Users should install this extension to streamline their data collection process, gain valuable insights from Shopify store data, and enhance their productivity.
